There is an ongoing tropical depression named Seventeen with a forecast track, expected maximum sustained winds, and minimum central pressure. The map displays the current position of the tropical depression near latitude 25.6 North, longitude 94.4 West, approximately 320 miles southwest of Lake Charles, Louisiana.
